==English==

===Noun===
'''polyandry'''

# The having of a plurality of [[husband]]s at the same time; usually, the marriage of a [[woman]] to more than one [[man]], or the practice of having several husbands, at the same time; -- opposed to [[monogamy]]; as, the nations of the East practiced '''polygamy'''. See the Note under [[bigamy]], and compare [[polygamy]] and [[polygyny]].

